Soptokachea sat varampoiki ek var. Hem utor ‘ adityovar ’ (adity = sury, var = dis) hea somskrit utravelean ailam. Haka moratthint ‘ rovivar ’ oxem mhonnttat. Ho suryopujek boro oxem manlam. Dhon-sompt'ti, sont'ti, bholaiki bori zaupak, dolleanche vikar axil'le ani zhuzant zoit melloupachi itsa dhorpi lok koslea na koslea prokaran hea disa sureachi upasona kortat. Vanjh bailo bhurgim zauchim mhunn hea disa suryourot kortat. Sureachi puza kortona oxttoul va xottkon heo akriti kaddttat. Aitarchea disa khoinchim kriteam kelear punnea melltta hevixincho brihojeotixosarantolo ek xlok oso-

